"title": "5290: defeat",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5290: defeat",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The overcoming of or being overcome by a physical, spiritual or circumstantial enemy. Those humbled before God by such a defeat eventually come to see it as a positive experience, leading to increased spiritual maturity. The way to avoid being defeated is to trust in God and to wear the spiritual armour he provides.</p>\n<h2>Defeat as the overcoming of enemies</h2>\n<h3>Physical enemies such as armies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:5-Gen14:6\">GEN 14:5–14:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:15\">GEN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen36:35\">GEN 36:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:4\">DEU 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:46\">DEU 4:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:1-Deut7:2\">DEU 7:1–7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:7\">DEU 29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:33\">JOS 10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:1-Josh11:9\">JOS 11:1–11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:19-Judg7:22\">JDG 7:19–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:10\">1SA 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:11\">1SA 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:48\">1SA 14:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:50\">1SA 17:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:17\">2SA 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:17-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:17–5:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:8-1Chr14:17\">1CH 14:8–14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:11\">PSA 92:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:10\">JER 37:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:15\">ZEC 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:1\">HEB 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:34\">HEB 11:34</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual enemies such as Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:19\">LUK 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:30\">JHN 14:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">ROM 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">COL 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">2TH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:13-1John2:14\">1JN 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:11\">REV 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2\">REV 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>The world as the realm of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:37\">ROM 8:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:21\">ROM 12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:4\">1JN 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:4-1John5:5\">1JN 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">REV 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26\">REV 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:5\">REV 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:12\">REV 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7\">REV 21:7</a></p>\n<h2>Defeat as being overcome by enemies</h2>\n<h3>By physical enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:17\">LEV 26:17</a></strong> <em>The Israelites were often defeated by their enemies as a punishment for disobeying God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:41-Num14:43\">NUM 14:41–14:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:42\">DEU 1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:25\">DEU 28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:4\">JOS 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:15\">JDG 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:12-Judg3:14\">JDG 3:12–3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:1-1Sam4:11\">1SA 4:1–4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:33\">1KI 8:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:24\">2CH 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:4\">PSA 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:9-Ps44:12\">PSA 44:9–44:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:62\">PSA 78:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:7-Jer19:9\">JER 19:7–19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:7\">JER 21:7</a></p>\n<h3>By spiritual enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:13-Jas1:15\">JAS 1:13–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6-Gen3:22\">GEN 3:6–3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:17\">2SA 11:2–11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:7\">1CO 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:18\">1TH 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:5\">1TH 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:11\">1TI 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:20\">2PE 2:20</a></p>\n<h3>By circumstances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:10\">PSA 39:10</a></strong> <em>This refers to God's chastisement through affliction</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:4\">PSA 32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:2\">PSA 38:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:5-2Sam22:6\">2SA 22:5–22:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:4-Ps18:5\">PSA 18:4–18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:1–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8-Job36:9\">JOB 36:8–36:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:9\">JER 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:16\">DAN 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:37\">LUK 8:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:21\">ROM 12:21</a></p>\n<h2>Defeat as a positive experience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:10\">JAS 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14-2Chr7:15\">2CH 7:14–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67\">PSA 119:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:71\">PSA 119:71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:9-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:9–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6\">1PE 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Defeat can be avoided</h2>\n<h3>By trusting in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:1-Ps25:3\">PSA 25:1–25:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:18\">2CH 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:5\">PSA 22:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:1-Ps31:4\">PSA 31:1–31:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:1-Ps71:3\">PSA 71:1–71:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:6-Ps112:8\">PSA 112:6–112:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1\">PSA 125:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:33\">ROM 9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:11\">ROM 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6\">1PE 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>By wearing the spiritual armour God provides</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:18\">EPH 6:10–6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12\">ROM 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a></p>",
